use onChange in the username class

add a string in the main login class :
String name = "";

Then add $name in front of welcome string 

and then 

Then use this in the TextFormField of the userName:

onChanged: (value){
                      name = value;
                      setState(() {});
                    },

setState calls the build the right way

This will add the text in front of welcome as you type it in the username box